title: U.S. Warnings to China on Arms Aid for Russia’s War Portend Global Rift
description: Secretary of State Antony J. Blinken says Washington has indications that Beijing is strongly considering giving military aid to Moscow for the war in Ukraine.

title: Your Monday Briefing: A Testy Exchange Between the U.S. and China
description: Also, Vladimir Putin’s war narrative takes hold in Russia.

title: Aging Societies
description: Asia’s population is shrinking faster than any other continent’s.

title: One Year Into War, Putin Is Crafting the Russia He Craves
description: In Ukraine, President Vladimir V. Putin’s invasion has met setback after setback. But its effect at home has been very different.

title: Zelensky Welcomes Pledges to Hold Russia Accountable for Crimes
description: The Ukrainian leader said he was grateful for Western statements of support, as Russia rejected American accusations that it had committed “crimes against humanity” in the war.

title: Despite Help for Venezuelans in South America, Many Still Head to U.S.
description: Colombia, with U.S. help, is providing temporary visas to Venezuelan migrants. Still, financial struggles are leading many to leave for the United States.

title: Despised Dictator’s ‘Scary’ Shrine Becomes a Bet on Albania’s Future
description: The enormous pyramid was long a reminder of both a brutal regime and the decades of disappointments that followed. Now, it’s a symbol of a city aspiring to be the high-tech “Tel Aviv of the Balkans.”

title: Why Milan’s Duomo Cathedral Is Still So Adored
description: The care for Milan’s cathedral has been nonstop since 1386, but despite the constant need for refurbishment, the beloved landmark’s hold on the city is unbreakable.

title: Syrian State Media Reports a Deadly Strike in Damascus
description: The news agency SANA and the Syrian Observatory for Human Rights said Israel was behind the bombing.

title: ‘Brainwashing a Generation’: British Schools Combat Andrew Tate’s Views
description: Alarmed by an online personality’s popularity among their students, educators are mobilizing to combat the sexism he promotes.
